---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="AI Agents and Digital Marketing for Rental Companies"
  description="Jonroc builds AI agents and runs digital marketing for party rental, tool rental, and equipment rental companies. Automated quotes, inventory management, and local SEO that wins bookings."
>
  <Header />

  <main id="main-content">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 pt-36 pb-24 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
        aria-hidden="true"
        style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 50% 30%, rgba(201,168,76,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);"
      ></div>

      <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="inline-block text-[#C9A84C] text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6 border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1">
          Rental Industry
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] leading-tight mb-8">
          AI Agents and Digital Marketing<br class="hidden md:block" />
          for <span class="text-[#C9A84C]">Rental Companies</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[#9CA3AF] max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Party rental, tool rental, equipment rental. Your entire business runs on speed: fast quotes, clean inventory, and customers who hear back before they call your competitor.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[#9CA3AF] max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-12">
          Jonroc installs the AI agents that handle the fast work and builds the digital presence that makes sure customers find you first.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-block btn-shine bg-[#C9A84C] text-[#0A0A0A] font-bold text-base px-10 py-5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#E2C070] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#C9A84C] focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-[#0A0A0A] transition-colors duration-200 shadow-xl shadow-[#C9A84C]/20"
          >
            Book a Free Discovery Call
          </a>
          <a
            href="#what-we-do"
            class="inline-block border border-white/20 text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold text-base px-10 py-5 rounded-full hover:border-white/40 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/30 transition-colors duration-200"
          >
            See What We Do
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pain Points -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-[#111111] relative">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-48 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#C9A84C]/40 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <p class="inline-block text-[#C9A84C] text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-5 border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1">
          The Real Problems
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-4 leading-tight">
          What's Costing You Bookings
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-lg mb-14 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          Rental businesses live and die by response time and logistics. Here's where the cracks usually are.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <!-- Pain Point 1 -->
          <div class="bg-[#1A1A1A] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-[#C9A84C]/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-3">Quotes Taking Too Long, Losing Customers to Faster Competitors</h3>
            <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed">
              Customer asks Friday afternoon. It sits until Monday. They booked someone else. In rental, quote speed is booking speed. Every hour you wait is a window for your competitor to close the deal.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Pain Point 2 -->
          <div class="bg-[#1A1A1A] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-[#C9A84C]/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 7.5l-.625 10.632a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.247 2.118H6.622a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.247-2.118L3.75 7.5M10 11.25h4M3.375 7.5h17.25c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125v-1.5c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125H3.375c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v1.5c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-3">Inventory Conflicts Discovered Too Late</h3>
            <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed">
              Equipment double-booked. Items that were supposed to be returned are still out. Damage from the last rental that nobody logged. Inventory conflicts discovered at the wrong moment turn into customer service disasters and lost revenue.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Pain Point 3 -->
          <div class="bg-[#1A1A1A] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-[#C9A84C]/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.5 8.25h9m-9 3H12m-9.75 1.51c0 1.6 1.123 2.994 2.707 3.227 1.129.166 2.27.293 3.423.379.35.026.67.21.865.501L12 21l2.755-4.133a1.14 1.14 0 0 1 .865-.501 48.172 48.172 0 0 0 3.423-.379c1.584-.233 2.707-1.626 2.707-3.228V6.741c0-1.602-1.123-2.995-2.707-3.228A48.394 48.394 0 0 0 12 3c-2.392 0-4.744.175-7.043.513C3.373 3.746 2.25 5.14 2.25 6.741v6.018Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-3">Customer Follow-Ups Falling Through the Cracks</h3>
            <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed">
              Confirmation emails that don't go out. Delivery windows that don't get confirmed. Return reminders that nobody sends. Every missed touchpoint is a customer who shows up unprepared or doesn't come back.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Pain Point 4 -->
          <div class="bg-[#1A1A1A] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-[#C9A84C]/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-3">Marketing Budget With No Measurable Return</h3>
            <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] leading-relaxed">
              Money goes into ads, a website, maybe some social posts. Nobody can tell you if any of it actually drove a booking. Without trackable results, you're just spending and hoping. That's not a marketing strategy.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What We Do -->
    <section id="what-we-do" class="py-24 bg-[#0A0A0A] relative">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-48 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#C9A84C]/40 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <p class="inline-block text-[#C9A84C] text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-5 border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1">
          What We Do
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-4 leading-tight">
          What Jonroc Does for<br class="hidden sm:block" />
          <span class="text-[#C9A84C]">Rental Companies</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-lg mb-14 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          Automation that keeps your operation tight, and marketing that keeps your calendar full.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
          <!-- AI Agents -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#C9A84C] mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904 9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09 3.09Z" />
                </svg>
              </span>
              AI Agents
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Quote automation.</span>
                  <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Agents turn around quotes automatically based on availability and pricing rules. No more waiting until Monday.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Inventory conflict detection.</span>
                  <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Agents flag scheduling conflicts, late returns, and availability issues before they cause problems.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Customer communication agents.</span>
                  <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Confirmation emails, delivery windows, return reminders. Every touchpoint handled automatically.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Logistics automation.</span>
                  <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Routing, crew assignments, equipment manifests. The prep work that burns hours runs mostly on autopilot.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Digital Marketing -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#C9A84C] mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 border border-[#C9A84C]/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 8.689c0-.864.933-1.406 1.683-.977l7.108 4.061a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 0 1.954l-7.108 4.061A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 3 16.811V8.69ZM12.75 8.689c0-.864.933-1.406 1.683-.977l7.108 4.061a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 0 1.954l-7.108 4.061a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.683-.977V8.69Z" />
                </svg>
              </span>
              Digital Marketing
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Websites that convert.</span>
                  <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Built for rental companies, with online inquiry forms, inventory displays, and clear calls to action.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">SEO for local rental searches.</span>
                  <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Show up when someone searches "party rental near me" or "equipment rental in [your city]."</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Ad campaigns with real ROI.</span>
                  <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Every ad dollar tied to bookings you can actually count. No more guessing whether it worked.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Execution, not just strategy.</span>
                  <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> We build it, run it, and keep it working. Your marketing actually happens.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Speed Matters -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-[#111111] relative overflow-hidden">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
        aria-hidden="true"
        style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(201,168,76,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);"
      ></div>
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-48 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#C9A84C]/40 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <p class="inline-block text-[#C9A84C] text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6 border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1">
          Speed Matters
        </p>
        <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#F0F0F0] font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
          "The first rental company to respond with a quote wins the booking. Period."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-lg leading-relaxed">
          We automate your quote process so you respond in minutes, not days. By the time your competitor is pulling up the inquiry on Monday morning, you've already confirmed the booking.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonial -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-[#0A0A0A] relative">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-48 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#C9A84C]/40 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <div class="text-[#C9A84C] text-5xl font-serif mb-6 leading-none" aria-hidden="true">"</div>
        <blockquote class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-[#F0F0F0] font-medium leading-relaxed mb-8">
          We have used Jonroc Websites and Online Marketing for more than one of our businesses over the past several years. We are pleased with the prompt attention we receive and the cooperative nature of the team.
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-[#C9A84C] font-semibold">Leann Rodgers</p>
        <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-sm mt-1">Rental Business Owner</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="py-28 bg-[#111111] relative overflow-hidden">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
        aria-hidden="true"
        style="background: url('/images/lattice-wide.jpg') repeat center / 400px 400px; opacity: 0.04;"
      ></div>
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
        aria-hidden="true"
        style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(201,168,76,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);"
      ></div>
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-48 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#C9A84C]/60 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="relative max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] leading-tight mb-6">
          Stop Losing Bookings<br class="hidden sm:block" />
          <span class="text-[#C9A84C]">to Slow Response Times</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          One call. No pitch deck. Let's look at your quote process and your online presence and find where the gaps are.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-block btn-shine bg-[#C9A84C] text-[#0A0A0A] font-bold text-base px-10 py-5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#E2C070] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#C9A84C] focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-[#111111] transition-colors duration-200 shadow-xl shadow-[#C9A84C]/20"
        >
          Book a Free Discovery Call
        </a>
        <p class="mt-5 text-[#9CA3AF]/50 text-sm">No commitment. No pressure.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
